title: Mateusz Morawiecki
deleted: On the 13th October, 2019, Morawiecki led PiS to victory in [[2019 Polish parliamentary election|that years parliamentary election]]. PiS won its highest ever vote in a parliamentary election to date, taking in 43.6% of the national vote and retaining majority government.
